headline: BTIG Lowers Coinbase (COIN ) PT to $340, Cites Expected Weakness in Q4 Transaction Volumes
summary: Coinbase Global Inc. (NASDAQ:COIN) is one of the most profitable new stocks to buy right now. On February 5, ahead of Coinbase’s Q4 2025 earnings report, BTIG lowered its price target for the stock to $340 from $420 while keeping a Buy rating.
